{"tid":1595050,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"改善熱門系統 增加行動標籖","createTime":"2019-09-26T01:01:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T16:56:11.000Z","uid":34208,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b6edcdfb8db07eccb946b074023979302899edc5","tid":1595050,"uid":34208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T01:01:04.000Z","msg":"鑒於行動post長期無法推上熱門/沉底<br />\n導致咗會員用bot嚟進行&rdquo;洗版式&rdquo;嘅方法嚟做宣傳<br />\n連仔琴日推出嘅反洗版政策無疑係可以解決到洗版妨礙閱讀嘅問題<br />\n但解決唔到行動post長期沉底呢個核心問題<br />\n<br />\n我建議連仔喺嚟緊一次嘅更新為時事/政務台加入<br />\n<strong>「行動」標籤</strong><br />\n並且畀呢類嘅post更加易上到熱門同埋可以延長佢哋留喺熱門嘅時間, 甚至頂置<br />\n會員亦可以用投訴機制決定該post有冇濫用行動標籤<br />\n<br />\n最後想多謝一眾LIHKG 嘅admin喺呢次運動作出嘅一切站務措施"},{"pid":"f27700a0c0111f1dad761dc5e8a4bb70790bccec","tid":1595050,"uid":34208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T01:01:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dcf95da35cc3779aa2321895a79eaa178b8568b7","tid":1595050,"uid":34208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T01:02:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb66bc7e0c5cb166784bffff43b09f8422d737dc","tid":1595050,"uid":34208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T01:02:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1709c7e8dcd39be772a8b80ae196f4610cdc6eec","tid":1595050,"uid":34208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T01:02:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"621deb8d55dba2a78c7fd60322ff49b201756f3c","tid":1595050,"uid":297356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T01:02:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65808c048e002eb5ec674e9ccbd9084b1fef3e5b","tid":1595050,"uid":69946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T01:02:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f49933376e50320e24c1117b0452ffc472edbfbb","tid":1595050,"uid":274435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T01:02:51.000Z","msg":"岩啊"},{"pid":"9c71c66b86e9c1a372ee7da8c3a5e8bcf8826ed9","tid":1595050,"uid":158546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,